Package asap.realizer Description

AsapRealizer core package. Contains:
  • the scheduler
  • pegboard
  • Engines: WaitEngine, ActivateEngine, ParameterValueChangeEngine, InterruptEngine
  • Interfaces for Engine, Planner, PlanUnit, etc
